‚Ä¢	National Inventors‚Äô Day (U.S.) ‚Äì Celebrated annually on Feb 11 in honor of inventors and innovators, coinciding with Thomas Edison‚Äôs birthday. It‚Äôs a day recognizing past and present inventors‚Äô contributions to progress.
‚Ä¢	Safer Internet Day ‚Äì Observed in the United States and many other countries on this day, aiming to raise awareness about online safety and responsible internet use. Schools, tech companies, and communities often hold events promoting safer digital practices.
